f_{XY}
f_{XY} = 1/(2x^2)
|x|>1
\int_0^\infty  {xf_{XY} (x)\,{\rm d}x}  = \int_1^\infty  {(2x)^{ - 1} \,{\rm d}x}  = \infty 
\int_{ - \infty }^0 {|x|f_{XY} (x)\,{\rm d}x}  = \int_{ - \infty }^{ - 1} {(2|x|)^{ - 1} \,{\rm d}x}  = \infty 
